{"tid":804310,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解決樓上噪音問題","createTime":"2018-09-03T02:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T13:24:56.000Z","uid":134093,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42889af6ff02055a20f339f9a33c868d20294682","tid":804310,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"咩方法都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條撚樣好醒目，每朝9點後就開始揼野鑽野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一到7點就停手<br />\n試過搵保安投訴，又搵過主任家訪<br />\n又報過警<br />\n上去屌柒佢，又死口唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7fa0d4615751f59ba2bd78166d7a081d2aa883","tid":804310,"uid":5475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"反制噪音裝置"},{"pid":"fefd3e00a45d8e8e848dd20ae05a2135d08e8701","tid":804310,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"製造更大既噪音"},{"pid":"90f1f3f8363ed1b29e32de5fa1fdb0115cef9028","tid":804310,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fefd3e00a45d8e8e848dd20ae05a2135d08e8701","tid":804310,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"製造更大既噪音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"樓下好難贏"},{"pid":"95b636fcd65db176812c4c87bbc1b4aa53fcaeba","tid":804310,"uid":195023,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"震樓神器可以幫到你"},{"pid":"483afb30bb809d0e94c6cfa9da9575760149fac6","tid":804310,"uid":171800,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"裝修聲唔一定係樓上，樓下鑽你一樣會覺得係樓上。"},{"pid":"7e68c86dfa93063262e52c2c1d04661e9310e82e","tid":804310,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"搬返佢上面"},{"pid":"903e26d40f3f620a61374bfd83b6bb93cfa93b62","tid":804310,"uid":172844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"我樓上又係咁<br />\n不過唔係裝修<br />\n係佢話仆街女成日係到跑跑跳跳<br />\n早午晚都係咁樣<br />\n試過上去屌鳩佢<br />\n佢話&quot;會唔會聽錯阿 我個女女好乖<br />\n會唔會係有鬼阿&quot;<br />\n明撚明望到入面佢係到跳緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都冇佢符<br />\n叫看更嚟睇又咁啱唔跳<br />\n報警係咁又驚比人話浪費警力<br />\n都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係話好嘈  但真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20532ed9bb078c48bb0fe3201aa5382c687bc904","tid":804310,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"日頭辦公時間係可以攞正牌裝修喎"},{"pid":"ee62d5456e7568214538d42e68f9931006ca181e","tid":804310,"uid":22708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"唉屌<br />\n樓上班細路又係成日跳<br />\n主任食蕉都搵過晒<br />\n差在未上去當面屌柒<br />\n但又驚正面衝突會令情況更壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c335a23c4fb27e0beb27964b448c0489b5c78964","tid":804310,"uid":105298,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"半年前隔離屋試過日日凌晨，用汽車喇叭黎播歌<br />\n又係報警投訴極都無用<br />\n結果第二朝我寫信放係佢信箱<br />\n內容大概話<br />\n再播歌搵黑社會搞鳩你全家<br />\n你個女都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一場鄰區，唔想佢出事就好自為知<br />\n結果呢半年收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfbe7e33d80f82fb8edf65fbb2fbcff347a77ac","tid":804310,"uid":176063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04239936a8f0fa9b3d4ccdd1243a606765eb3194","tid":804310,"uid":105298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1bfbe7e33d80f82fb8edf65fbb2fbcff347a77ac","tid":804310,"uid":176063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c335a23c4fb27e0beb27964b448c0489b5c78964","t